==Spanish==

===Etymology===
From Latin [[aperire]].

===Transitive verb===
'''abrir'''

# to [[open]]
#: ''Por favor, '''abre''' la ventana Jorge.'' - "Please open the window George"
# to [[unlock]]
#: ''Yo '''abro''' la cerradura.'' - "I unlock the lock."
# to [[turn on]]
#: ''El '''abrió''' el llave.'' - "He turned on the faucet."

===Conjugation===
''Irregular in the past participle.''

